'''瑞秋·莎拉·比爾森'''（{{lang-en|Rachel Sarah Bilson}}，{{bd|1981年|8月25日|catIdx=Bilson, Rachel}}），美國女演員。她生長於[[加州|加州]]的演藝家庭，2003年正式踏入演藝圈，隨後以演出[[黃金時段|黃金時段]][[戲劇|影集]]《[[玩酷世代|玩酷世代]]》中[[莎瑪·羅伯茨|莎瑪·羅伯茨]]一角廣獲矚目。2006年，她以電影《[[終情之吻|終情之吻]]》首度跨足大螢幕，其他作品包括2008年科幻動作電影《[[移動世界|移動世界]]》。

== 個人生活 ==
比爾森曾和《[[玩酷世代|玩酷世代]]》同劇演員[[亞當·布洛迪|亞當·布洛迪]]交往三年，直到2006年結束感情<ref>[http://www.people.com/people/article/0,26334,1566162,00.html Rachel Bilson and Adam Brody split] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011032118/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,26334,1566162,00.html |date=2007-10-11 }}. [2009-11-15].</ref>。2007年，她因為拍攝《[[移動世界|移動世界]]》而和[[海登·克里斯唐森|海登·克里斯唐森]]結緣，翌年訂婚<ref>[http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20259778,00.html Rachel Bilson and Hayden Christensen are engaged] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/65pTUXiLL?url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20259778,00.html |date=20120301032857 |dateformat=iso }}. [2009-04-20].</ref>。他們在2010年曾因故分手，但數個月後又復合。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/healthylifestyle/news/engaged-rachel-bilson-hayden-christensen-taking-a-break-1970241|title=Engaged Rachel Bilson, Hayden Christensen "Taking a Break"|accessdate=2010-06-18|work=[[US_Weekly|US Weekly]]|archive-date=2010-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100621114100/http://www.usmagazine.com/healthylifestyle/news/engaged-rachel-bilson-hayden-christensen-taking-a-break-1970241|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nypost.com/p/pagesix/rachel_bilson_taking_break_from_1wDi3FR5FjaSuqIBdoXNFP|title=Rachel Bilson 'taking a break' from fiance Hayden Christensen|accessdate=2010-06-18|work=[[New_York_Post|New York Post]]|date=2010-06-17|archive-date=2012-03-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65pTWT47L?url=http://www.nypost.com/p/pagesix/rachel_bilson_taking_break_from_1wDi3FR5FjaSuqIBdoXNFP|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Shira|first=Dahvi|date=2010-08-09|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20408970,00.html|title=Hayden Christensen & Rachel Bilson Called off the  Engagement|accessdate=2010-08-10|work=People.com|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303175851/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20408970,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.nydailynews.com/gossip/2010/11/09/2010-11-09_rachel_bilson_and_hayden_christensen_dating_again_months_after_calling_off_engag.html Rachel Bilson and Hayden Christensen 'dating again' months after calling off engagement] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/gossip/2010/11/09/2010-11-09_rachel_bilson_and_hayden_christensen_dating_again_months_after_calling_off_engag.html |date=20101113065909 }}. [2010-11-09].</ref>

比爾森是部分媒體所公認的「時尚迷」<ref name="penterprise">{{cite web| last =Pearson| first =Ryan| authorlink =| coauthors =| title =Rachel Bilson, fashion junkie| publisher =PE.com| date =2006-09-20| url =http://www.pe.com/entertainment/stories/PE_Fea_Ent_D_movie.bilsson.23a970b.html| accessdate =2007-01-20| archive-date =2007-09-29| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20070929083316/http://www.pe.com/entertainment/stories/PE_Fea_Ent_D_movie.bilsson.23a970b.html| dead-url =no}}</ref><ref name="horizons">{{cite web| last =Fischer| first =Paul| authorlink =| coauthors =| title =Interview: Rachel Bilson "The Last Kiss"| publisher =Dark Horizons| date =2006-08-22| url =http://www.darkhorizons.com/news06/bilson.php| format =| accessdate =2007-01-20| archive-date =2008-12-01| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20081201181416/http://www.darkhorizons.com/news06/bilson.php| dead-url =no}}</ref><ref name="fmovies">{{cite web| last =Guest| first =| authorlink =| coauthors =| title =Rachel Bilson The Last Kiss Q&A| publisher =FutureMovies| url =http://www.futuremovies.co.uk/filmmaking.asp?ID=185| format =| accessdate =2007-01-20| date =October 2006| archive-date =2013-08-09| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20130809142728/http://www.futuremovies.co.uk/filmmaking.asp?ID=185| dead-url =no}}</ref>。她將自己的穿著歸類為「復古」路線，並自言受到[[凱特·摩絲|凱特·摩絲]]和[[黛安·基頓|黛安·基頓]]的影響<ref name="fmovies" />。她的衣著亦時常融入[[波西米亞風|波西米亞風]]。2007年，她和[[DKNY|DKNY]]牛仔褲接觸，產生了建立流行時尚品牌、設計系列服裝的念頭<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sassybella.com/index.php/2008/03/13/rachel-bilson-to-design-edie-rose-collection-for-dkny-jeans/ |title=Rachel Bilson to design Edie Rose collection for DKNY Jeans |publisher=Sassybella.com |date=2008-03-13 |accessdate=2008-10-25 |archive-date=2008-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080611053857/http://www.sassybella.com/index.php/2008/03/13/rachel-bilson-to-design-edie-rose-collection-for-dkny-jeans/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。於是他們成立了「Edie Rose」時尚品牌，並在2008年9月首度發表作品。此系列服飾以黑白兩色為基調，間或以顯眼的鮮黃色作為點綴，易於結合衣櫥內現有衣物進行穿搭。她的主打概念是以低於100美元的實惠價格，讓年輕女生也能擁有時髦單品<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.accesshollywood.com/rachel-bilson/rachel-bilson-launches-edie-rose-for-dkny-jeans_video_738481 |title=Rachel Bilson Launches Edie Rose For DKNY Jeans |publisher=accesshollywood.com |access-date=2011-09-16 |archive-date=2011-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110913002641/http://www.accesshollywood.com/rachel-bilson/rachel-bilson-launches-edie-rose-for-dkny-jeans_video_738481 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他們在2008年7月推出廣告圖，由比爾森擔任自己品牌的服裝模特兒<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sassybella.com/index.php/2008/07/21/rachel-bilson-models-her-edie-rose-line-for-dkny-jeans/ |title=Rachel Bilson models her Edie Rose line for DKNY Jeans |publisher=Sassybella.com |date=2008-03-13 |accessdate=2008-10-25 |archive-date=2008-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081202041202/http://www.sassybella.com/index.php/2008/07/21/rachel-bilson-models-her-edie-rose-line-for-dkny-jeans |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她在《[[青少年時尚|青少年時尚]]》雜誌訪談中提到：「我想把這件事和演員的瑞秋·比爾森劃分得越清楚越好。我希望人們是真的欣賞這些衣服，而不是它們背後的人物<ref>[http://www.teenvogue.com/industry/fashionwork/2008/10/youngstars Rachel Bilson Edie Rose Interview] {{Wayback|url=http://www.teenvogue.com/industry/fashionwork/2008/10/youngstars |date=20120401105642 }}. [2009-04-10].</ref>。」她的住家在2009年5月遭竊，屋內許多流行服飾皆被洗劫一空<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20279925,00.html|title=Rachel Bilson's L.A. Home Is Burglarized|author=Alexis Chiu|publisher=People|access-date=2011-09-16|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194807/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20279925,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此外，比爾森曾多次拒絕半裸登上[[男性雜誌|男性雜誌]]，表示她覺得自己的身體是「神聖的」，「不是放在那裡讓全世界看的<ref name="starpulsenews1006">{{cite web| last =| first =| authorlink =| coauthors =| title =Rachel Bilson Believes Her Body Is Sacred & Only for Boyfriend To See| publisher =StarPulse.com| date =2006-10-10| url =http://www.starpulse.com/news/index.php/2006/10/10/rachel_bilson_believes_her_body_is_sacre| format =| accessdate =2007-01-20| archive-date =2007-06-29| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20070629233155/http://www.starpulse.com/news/index.php/2006/10/10/rachel_bilson_believes_her_body_is_sacre| dead-url =no}}</ref>。」但她後來接受為《Maxim》雜誌拍攝照片。比爾森的時尚態度和處世風格使她成為犯罪集團[[Bling_Ring|Bling Ring]]的目標；他們曾多次入竊她的住屋。<ref name="ABC1">{{Cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/2020/TheLaw/bling-ring-celebrity-hollywood-burglaries-cops/story?id=9999401&page=1 |title=ABC News: "Exclusive: Inside Hollywood's 'Bling Ring'" page 1 |access-date=2011-09-16 |archive-date=2020-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320150211/https://abcnews.go.com/2020/TheLaw/bling-ring-celebrity-hollywood-burglaries-cops/story?id=9999401&page=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="VF4">{{Cite web |url=http://www.vanityfair.com/culture/features/2010/03/billionaire-girls-201003?currentPage=4 |title=Vanity Fair: "The Suspects Wore Louboutins" Page 4 |accessdate=2011-09-16 |archive-date=2013-03-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6F38w1W7s?url=http://www.vanityfair.com/culture/features/2010/03/billionaire-girls-201003?currentPage=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

